There are generally four classes of software used to support the [[Six Sigma]] process improvement protocol: *Analysis tools, which are used to perform statistical or process analysis; *Program management tools, used to manage and track a corporation's entire Six Sigma program; *DMAIC and Lean online project collaboration tools for local and global teams; *Data Collection tools that feed information directly into the analysis tools and significantly reduce the time spent gathering data.
